text: This was '19. I just went back a few months. May do more if we continue to wait for actual news...

text: President Trump arrived at his golf club in West Palm Beach shortly after 9 a.m. He has nothing on his public schedule for today.
author: jfritze

text: What's the longest @realDonaldTrump has gone without tweeting? In the past six months it looks like 22 hours is the record. That was in early February, between tweets about a caravan and announcing David Bernhardt for Interior. We're currently at 16 hours and about 15 minutes.
author: jfritze

text: Giuliani tells us Trump's legal team hasn't been briefed on the report. “It keeps it appropriate,” he said.
author: jfritze

text: White House has just called a lid, which means we don't expect to see or hear from the president tonight about the Mueller report -- or anything else.
author: jfritze

text: Robert Mueller has completed his investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 election, delivering a report that signals the end of the long-running inquiry that loomed over the first two years of Donald Trump's presidency.
author: jfritze
